Day 67: Deploy Guest Book App on Kubernetes

Date: November 2, 2025
Overview
Deployed complete multi-tier application (frontend, Redis master, Redis slaves).
Key Concepts Learned

Complete application architecture
Master-slave patterns
Service discovery
Production deployment practices

Challenges Faced
Coordinating multiple deployments and services. This was the culmination of all Kubernetes learning!

Summary
Days 48-67 were the most challenging yet rewarding! Kubernetes is complex, but mastering pods, deployments, services, volumes, 
and troubleshooting transformed me into a confident K8s operator. These 20 days built the foundation for container orchestration at scale.
